HEADWORD: Mutilation
<hw>Mu`ti*la"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>mutilatio</ets>: cf. F. <ets>mutilation</ets>.]</ety> <def>The act
